desc: Fun statement acrylic jewellery, handmade by a bush business in Winton, the dinosaur capital of Australia by vertebrate paleontologist Adele Pentland.

layout.text:
Whimsical jewellery handmade by a paleontologist in Winton, rural QLD.
From dinosaurs to pop culture & everything in between, there's colourful, comfortable earrings that can jazz up even the dullest work uniform.
